---
title: Chicken Breast, Cheese and Pea Penne Bake with Bacon Crumb
description: This Chicken Breast, Cheese and Spinach Penne Bake is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R03_W10_UK_R3416-31_Main_low-11a17cd8.jpg
